<P>
   The N.Y. Times plans a package of stories on the resignation of
Tina Brown as editor of The New Yorker:
</P>
<P>
   BROWN-RESIGN (New York) _ A ledeall on the resignation and what
we know of its circumstances. She is leaving to develop a new
magazine for Walt Disney's Miramax. By Geraldine Fabrikant and
Janny Scott.
</P>
<P>
