<HEADLINE>
(RESENDING TO FIX BYLINE) 
NOW IS THE SUMMER OF OUR MALCONTENT
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By TIM MADIGAN 
c.1998 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
