   7. ``The Children'' by Edith Wharton
</P>
<P>
   8. ``The Devil and Daniel Webster'' by Stephen Vincent Benet
</P>
<P>
   9. ``Farewell, My Lovely'' by Raymond Chandler
</P>
<P>
   10. ``Flotsam'' by Erich Maria Remarque
</P>
<P>
   11. ``Glory for Me'' by Mackinlay Kantor
</P>
<P>
   12. ``Little Pinks'' by Damon Runyon
</P>
<P>
   13. ``The Magnificent Bastards'' by Lucy Herndon Crockett
</P>
<P>
   14. ``The Man of Property'' by John Galsworthy
</P>
<P>
   15. ``Rome Haul'' by Walter D. Edmonds
</P>
<P>
   16. ``Sanctuary'' by William Faulkner
</P>
<P>
   17. ``Shoeless Joe'' by W.P. Kinsella
</P>
<P>
   18. ``To Have and Have Not'' by Ernest Hemingway
</P>
<P>
   19. ``Uncle Wiggily in Connecticut'' by J.D. Salinger
</P>
<P>
   20. ``Years Are So Long'' by Josephine Lawrence
</P>
<P>
   Titles of the film versions:
</P>
<P>
   a. ``All That Money Can Buy''
</P>
