<SLUG> BC-KEYRATES-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
KEY RATES 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (Repeating for all needing.) (mk) 
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   Here are the daily key rates from The New York Times.
</P>
<P>
   ------------------Wednesday----Previous day---Year Ago
</P>
<P>
   PRIME RATE ---------- 8.50 ------ 8.50 ------- 8.50
</P>
<P>
   DISCOUNT RATE ------- 5.00 ------ 5.00 ------- 5.00
</P>
<P>
   FEDERAL FUNDS(x) ---- 5.44 ------ 5.56 ------- 5.44
</P>
<P>
   3-MO. TREAS. BILLS -- 4.94 ------ 4.95 ------- 4.96
</P>
<P>
