<HEADLINE>
SHOPPING FOR HEMP 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 (WITH HEMP-ART) 
 By ANNE. M. SPITZA  
 c.1998 The Arizona Republic  
<TEXT>
<P>
   (Undated) - Although hemp products are relatively prolific, they
are not always readily available. Major manufacturers are dabbling
in hemp, but the bulk of hemp retail goods is coming from
cottage-industry companies.
</P>
<P>
   As such, hemp-driven Internet shopping sites and mail-order
catalogs are abundant. A bit of Web crawling and statewide
wandering uncovered the following finds:
</P>
<P>
   _ The Frederick Brewing Co. in Maryland uses hemp seeds in
brewing its Hempen Gold cream ale and a Hemp ale. (301) 694-7899 or
www.fredbrew.com
</P>
<P>
   _ The Rella Good Cheese Co. in Santa Rosa, Calif., sells hemp
tofu and hemp-seed veggie burgers. 800-656-9669 or www.rella.com
</P>
<P>
   _ The Oxford Hemp Exchange offers reusable hemp coffee filters
as well as hemp-flour hotcake, pizza and cookie dough mixes.
800-411-5728 or www.pbmo.net/oxhemp/
</P>
<P>
   _ Earth Runnings in Taos, N.M., sells handcrafted hemp
bedspreads, sheets, shower curtains and pillows. (505) 758-5703 or
earthrun(at)laplaza.org
</P>
<P>
   _ The Hemptech Web site (www/hemptech.com) lists more than 400
hemp products under the categories automotive, body care, paper,
plastics, clothing and food.
</P>
<P>
   _ In Arizona, hemp boutiques have opened in several low-key
locales. There is Southwest Hemp Co. in Prescott, Hemp &AMP; Hawg in
Sedona and Flagstaff Hemp Co. in Flagstaff.
</P>
<P>
   _ The Crucial Creations clothing manufacturer in Tucson, Ariz.,
markets dresses, shirts, jackets and jeans worldwide via retail
stores and a catalog. 800-HEMP-4US _ 800-436-7487.
</P>
<P>
   _CHA (Coalition for Hemp Awareness) in Chandler Heights, Ariz.,
sells Thomas Jefferson-style shirts, cowboy dusters, ponchos and
hats 602-988-9355.
</P>
<P>
   _ AZIDA, a hemp body-products manufacturer in Elfrida, Ariz.,
makes hemp-oil shower gels, moisturizers and sunscreens
800-603-6601. &QL;
</P>
</TEXT>
