<HEADLINE>
 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 BC-ADD-BUDGET-AZR 
  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients) 
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   The following Arizona Republic column has been added for use by
clients of the NYTimes News Service for Thursday, July 9. If you
have any questions, please contact the Republic News Desk at (602)
444-8286.
</P>
<P>
   &QL;
</P>
<P>
   MONTINI-COLUMN (Undated) - A company in Orland, Ill., plans to
sell copies of Abraham Zapruder's home movie of the assassination
of John Fitzgerald Kennedy. The expected price is $19.98 for a VHS
tape and $24.98 for a digital video disc. If you buy one, you are a
pig. By E.J.MONTINI. Story will move in the ``A'' and ``K''
categories. &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
