visit to Russia's Mir space station, astronaut Andy Thomas says
he's regaining the physical strength drained by 141 days of
weightlessness. Thomas' return June 12 signaled the start of a
lengthy rehabilitation effort to rebuild his bones and muscles as
well as retune his nervous system to gravity. By MARK CARREAU.
(Already filed)
