<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-07-08 21:16 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6425 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BROWN-HOLLYWOOD-NYT &LR;      07-08 0956
